Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you are a senior theater studies major with a senior project, then yes, you should take this class.

No choice on taking this one, but try to invest deeply in your fellow students' work, and also to critique Senior Projects with honesty and frankness (along with respect). Tepidness helps nobody. Also, use your design presentation as an actual tool to check in with your designers and to make sure that the full aesthetic of your show will be cohesive. In your post-mortem, ask bluntly about the areas of the show which you are most wary/unsure about the success of; use criticism as an actual opportunity to grow and improve.
